      <h1>Smart Data Guidebook (DBT)</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        The Department for Business and Trade is developing a cross-sector Smart
        Data Guidebook — chapter-by-chapter guidance for how Smart Data schemes
        (property, open banking, open energy, etc.) should handle identity,
        governance, security, and interoperability under the
        <a href="/governance/legislation">Data (Use and Access) Act 2025</a>.
        This page tracks each chapter draft as DBT circulates it for review,
        alongside our own notes on how it relates to PDTF. See also
        <a href="/governance/departments#dbt">Departments &amp; bodies — DBT</a>
        for DBT's other Smart Data workstreams (Council, Roadmap, Challenge).
      </p>

      <h2 id="chapter5">Chapter 5 — Security, Risk and Fraud Management</h2>

      <p>
        First draft circulated 10 July 2026, for review and input by
        <strong>Friday 24 July 2026</strong>. Working Session 1 was held
        6 July 2026 (Teams), ahead of the draft's circulation; Session 2 is
        scheduled for 13 July 2026.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <a class="resource-link" href="/resource?path=source/02-policy-and-positioning/opda-reports/sd-guidebook-chapter-5/SMART DATA GUIDEBOOK_Chapter 5 Security, Risk and Fraud Management_V1.pdf"><code>Chapter 5 draft (PDF)</code></a>
          — also available as
          <a class="resource-link" href="/resource?path=source/02-policy-and-positioning/opda-reports/sd-guidebook-chapter-5/SMART DATA GUIDEBOOK_Chapter 5 Security, Risk and Fraud Management_V1.docx"><code>.docx</code></a>.
        </li>
        <li>
          <a class="resource-link" href="/resource?path=source/02-policy-and-positioning/opda-reports/sd-guidebook-chapter-5/SD Guidebook Minutes (External Use) - Chapter 5 Session 1.pdf"><code>Session 1 minutes (PDF)</code></a>
          — also available as
          <a class="resource-link" href="/resource?path=source/02-policy-and-positioning/opda-reports/sd-guidebook-chapter-5/SD Guidebook Minutes (External Use) - Chapter 5 Session 1.docx"><code>.docx</code></a>.
          See also <a href="/engagement/meetings-decisions#sdGuidebook">Meetings &amp; decisions — Smart Data Guidebook sessions</a>.
        </li>
